OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F346A1784305119
OL,3,CMajor plans to redevelop Derby
OL,4,CAssembly Rooms given the go-ahead
OL,6,FA #100 million redevelopment of
OL,7,FDerby's Market Place to replace the
OL,8,FAssembly Rooms has got the go-ahead.
OL,10,FDerby City Council submitted major
OL,11,Fplans to redevelop the city centre
OL,12,Farea with new buildings and public
OL,13,Fopen space.
OL,15,FThe approval at a Derby planning
OL,16,Fmeeting on Thursday, July 16, moves
OL,17,Fthe replacement of the Assembly Rooms
OL,18,Fforward, following a long period of
OL,19,Funcertainty. It has stood empty for
OL,20,Fmore than a decade after a fire.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
