PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F346A1784305119
OL,3,CMajor plans to redevelop Derby
OL,4,CAssembly Rooms given the go-ahead
OL,6,FThe demolition of the Assembly Rooms
OL,7,Fhad already been approved, subject to
OL,8,Fconditions.
OL,10,FThe outline application for
OL,11,Fconsideration focused solely on the
OL,12,Fcreation of a new mixed-use building,
OL,13,Fnew office space, and a four-star
OL,14,Fhotel, once the former entertainment
OL,15,Fvenue is demolished.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,347,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F346A1784305119
OL,3,CMajor plans to redevelop Derby
OL,4,CAssembly Rooms given the go-ahead
OL,6,FThe council's Labour leadership group
OL,7,Fhave been keen to push forward the
OL,8,Fregeneration plans, with council
OL,9,Fleader Nadine Peatfield previously
OL,10,Fstating that she wanted work to start
OL,11,Fas soon as possible.
OL,13,FBut, despite approval, council bosses
OL,14,Ftold the meeting there will still be
OL,15,Ffurther hurdles to jump through before
OL,16,Fdemolition of the Assembly Rooms could
OL,17,Factually start.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
