CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F346A1784305119
OL,3,CMajor plans to redevelop Derby
OL,4,CAssembly Rooms given the go-ahead
OL,6,FA decision on the outline plans was
OL,7,Fexpected at a planning meeting in May,
OL,8,Fbut a slender majority of councillors
OL,9,Fwanted to defer the item after raising
OL,10,Fdesign concerns.
OL,12,FIt was heard at Thursday's meeting how
OL,13,Fbehind-the-scenes talks between the
OL,14,Fdevelopers and councillors were
OL,15,F"really helpful" and tweaks were made
OL,16,Fto the design in response to
OL,17,Fconversations.
OL,26,@wD@AOUwD@PO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/7
