OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,347,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F346A1784305119
OL,3,CMajor plans to redevelop Derby
OL,4,CAssembly Rooms given the go-ahead
OL,6,FCouncillor Martin Rawson said: "I
OL,7,Freally like these proposals.
OL,8,FAttractive shops and cafes will draw
OL,9,Fpeople to the area and that's what it
OL,10,Fneeds.
OL,12,F"It is sorely needed. Assembly Rooms
OL,13,Fhas been rotting for 10 years ` we
OL,14,Fneed to grasp the metal and bring this
OL,15,Fpart of the city centre back to life."
OL,17,FCouncillor Lucy Care, who was chairing
OL,18,Fthe meeting, said: "I see no reason
OL,19,Ffor a further deferral."
OL,26,@nD@`OUpD@YrrtD@AOUwD@fO]zD@TOU{D@XO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
