PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F346A1784305119
OL,3,CMajor plans to redevelop Derby
OL,4,CAssembly Rooms given the go-ahead
OL,6,FHowever, Councillor Matthew Holmes
OL,7,Fsaid he had concerns regarding the
OL,8,Fproject as a whole.
OL,10,FThe Mickleover councillor said: "You
OL,11,Fcan never have no risk, but this does
OL,12,Fcarry risk.
OL,14,F"Things can go wrong (such as)
OL,15,Fpandemic, war, supply issues. It (the
OL,16,Fphasing of the development) does
OL,17,Fconcern me. There's a lot of cogs in
OL,18,Fthis machine."
OL,26,@rD@aOUvD@AOUvD@VpmvD@^pnwD@bpmxD@[pnzD@
OL,26,ANO]
